content.title: Isinxibelelanisi sokufikelela
content.howToUseTooltip:
Apha ngezantsi kukho ezinye iimpawu zokumakisha kule ndawo inokusetyenziselwa ukukhetha imisebenzi, njengokuchofoza, ukuzalisa isicatshulwa, njl.

Ixabiso lokubonisa linokuphinda iphindwe kwiphepha le-App. Ukuba uhlangabezana nako uphindaphindile, nceda ugqithise ezinye iindlela zophawu ukumisela ubuchwephesha.

Ilizwi elibomvu libonisa ukuba ixabiso lokubonisa liyaphindwa, igama eliluhlaza libonisa ukuba ixabiso lokubonisa lahlukile kwi-pheng iphepha langoku, kwaye igama elimnyama libonisa ukuba akukho thelekiso luphindaphindiweyo.
